messages.text: Are you ignoring my calls?
Mel? WTF is going on??
Sorry. It’s hard for me to talk on the phone.
I’ve been hearing this weird ringing.
Did you go to Health Services?
No…it’s not that bad.
If you say so.
Did you tell Anders about the itching and the skin thing??
I did.
It was super awkward.
Where is he? I haven’t seen him in weeks.
I think he straight up dropped Prof. Hasbro’s class.
He wouldn’t tell me.
What a fucking weirdo.
COLLEGE ALERTS: A RARE STRAIN OF MENENGITIS HAS BEEN REPORTED ON CAMPUS.
PLEASE REPORT TO HEALTH SERVICES IMMEDIATELY IF YOU ARE EXPEREINCING ANY OF THE FOLLOWING SYMPTOMS:
PEELING SKIN, CHILLS, SENSITIVITY TO SOUND, SENSITIVITY TO LIGHT, OR FULL-BODY ITCHING
Did you get that message too?
Yeah.
Ummmm aren’t those like pretty much the EXACT symptoms you were experiencing?
I mean, kind of…
So it’s not an STD.
You were worried you’d contracted something from Anders.
No, it’s just a rare strain of some disease.
That was sarcasm by the way.
Anders told me that I have to contact all the people I had sex with since him.
I like how he just assumes that I sleep with all these guys.
Well...
Well, what?
You do have a few gentlemen callers.
Yeah but that’s none of his business. It’s not really yours, either.
I mean, have you hooked up with anyone since him??
Ugh. Kind of. No, I mean, not technically.
WHOOOOOOO?!
You have got to tell me!
Please.
No.
FINE.
I’ll find out though.
So do you want me to come with you to health services or what?
Why would I need you to come with me?
Because I’m your best friend??
I’m not going to health services. I’m fine.
Wait, seriously? You HAVE symptoms, Mel!
Just yesterday you were complaining about the fluorescent lights.
You wore sunglasses to the lab.
That was probably a migraine or something.
What’s gotten into you M? You’ve always been pro-doctor.
You’re studying to be one, after all...
I don’t trust Health Services.
Dr. Roberts creeps me out, with that weird moustache.
Wait. Did Anders tell you something else?
It’s a yes or no question, it shouldn’t take you that long to reply.
He said not to go. He said they were giving out poison pills.
Whoa.
I always thought that dude was a little weird but...
all I have to say to that is NOPE.
You don’t get it. He told me that this would happen.
That they would say it was Meningitis.
He’s telling you NOT to go to the doctor. That’s a problem.
I knew you’d be like this.
Like what?
Judgy. You hate all the guys I hook up with.
I don’t HATE anyone.
You do. You always have nasty things to say about them.
Remember Robert?
Robert was a creep.
He was eccentric.
He would collect the strands of hair you left on his pillow and keep them in that weird box of his.
I think that’s a little more than eccentric.
It was sweet! And you scared him off when you told him you knew about it!
I did you a favor.
You’re worse than my mom.
I’m going to pretend you didn’t say that.
Also...you should know...
I went to Health Services. I took those antibiotics.
WHAT?!
How long ago was this???
Why didn’t you tell me??
Like 2 weeks ago...
I was embarrassed, ok?
That skin thing was gross.
And they worked?
I’m texting you, aren’t I?
You know, fuck Anders.
Spreading his paranoia.
We should do something about it.
Let’s make him more paranoid.
How? He said he was changing phones.
But I bet you he’s still checking his Snapchat.
Hmm...
Post something on there. Say you took the pills.
That you didn’t listen to him. That you don’t think you have much longer.
Tell him you love him.
He’ll feel so guilty.
YES. Omg do it now.
Ok. Done. How do I look??
You look so…consumptive.
Like a Victorian babe.
Almost green, actually...
That will show him!
It’s not bad luck to fake your own death?
No one’s faking their own death. You’re just saying you took the pills.
Holy shit.
What?
Go on FB.
Now.
Oh my god. Charles Jansen died!!!
It looks like it was from meningitis.
Wait, did you know him?
That was the guy!!
What guy??
The one I hooked up with after Anders!
I’m so sorry Mel. That’s just…
I don’t even know what to say.
Just PLEASE go to health services.
They’re saying he went untreated for too long!
And that’s why the antibiotics didn’t work!!
I’ve got two options here.
I can trust the school, and go take their medicine, and maybe die...
Or I can trust Anders, and NOT take the medicine, and maybe die...
Do you see why I’m freaking out??
But I took the pills too! I’m fine!!!
That’s true. But still...idk.
So you’re trusting some random guy you slept with and not your best friend?
I don’t know Sasha. I’ve got some stuff to figure out.
I’ll text you soon, ok??
Fine. But Mel?
Yes??
I don’t think I could live with myself if I lost you.
